Sentencas: The oxide-ion conducting system (La1-xSrx)(2)Mo(1.5)W(0.5)O(9-delta)withx = 0.00, 0.02, 0.05 and 0.07 were prepared for the first time by modified polyol-mediated synthesis method.
Titulo: Modified polyol-mediated synthesis of Sr- and W-substituted La2Mo2O9solid electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The structural properties and electrical conductivity of this system (La1-xSrx)(2)Mo(1.5)W(0.5)O(9-delta)were studied using XRD, DT/TGA, SEM, XPS, BET, TEC and EIS characterization techniques.
Titulo: Modified polyol-mediated synthesis of Sr- and W-substituted La2Mo2O9solid electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It was found that doping of Sr and W together at La and Mo site, respectively, stabilizes the cubic beta-phase of La(2)Mo(2)O(9)at room temperature.
Titulo: Modified polyol-mediated synthesis of Sr- and W-substituted La2Mo2O9solid electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of system was found to be maximum forx = 0.05 doping of Sr at La site in (La1-xSrx)(2)Mo1.5W0.5O9-delta.
Titulo: Modified polyol-mediated synthesis of Sr- and W-substituted La2Mo2O9solid electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In dilatometry measurement, TEC was found to be 13.9 x 10(-6)/degrees C for the compositionsx = 0.05 which is compatible with a few other reported components of the intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC).
Titulo: Modified polyol-mediated synthesis of Sr- and W-substituted La2Mo2O9solid electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This synthesis route also helps for the preparation of fine grains, high specific surface area and reduced particle size at relatively lower calcination temperatures.
Titulo: Modified polyol-mediated synthesis of Sr- and W-substituted La2Mo2O9solid electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells
